                          Efficacy Research

                          Discover studies showing positive and impactful results of Edmentum programs on student learning, including those that meet What Works Clearinghouse standards and ESSA tiers of evidence.

                          Demonstrations of our effectiveness

                          You evaluate your programs based on the learning outcomes they deliver. View efficacy research which finds that our curricula and assessments improve student achievement.

                          ESSA Tier 2 Research

                          Students who successfully completed at least one Courseware course demonstrated higher rates of attendance and punctuality, and higher average grades by the end of the semester.

                          ESSA Tier 2 Research
